<div class="main_content">
    <div class="content_header">
        {{#each film}}
        <h1>{{this.title}}</h1>
        <p><span class="rating_span">Add review</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="content_main">
        <div class="left_main">
            <img src="../img/{{this.id}}.jpg" width="100%">
        </div>
        <div class="right_main">
            <div class="info">
                <p><b>Duration</b>: 2h 56m</p>
                <p><b>Release year</b>: 2022</p>
                <p><b>Actors</b>: Robert pattinson, ZoÃ« Kravitz, Bill Finger</p>
                <p><b>Director</b>: Matt Reeves</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info_2">
                <p><span class="watchlist_span">+ Watchlist</span></p>
                <p>Starring: 4.2/5</p>
                <p>IMDb: 8.4/10</p>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content_footer">
        <div class="footer_tag">
            <p><span class="tag_span">Action</span></p>
            <p><span class="tag_span">Crime</span></p>
            <p><span class="tag_span">Drama</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer_description">
            <p>When the Riddler, a sadistic serial killer, begins murdering key political figures in Gotham, Batman is forced to investigate the city's hidden corruption and question his family's involvement.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr>
    {{/each}}
    <br>
</div>